## Feature: LangFuse Enhanced Management Dashboard + GitLab-Triggered Prompt Merging

You are implementing the first major feature module of the internal AI Platform 
Management application. This module wraps and extends LangFuse to provide:

1. A richer visualization layer over LangFuse's native UI
2. An automated prompt merge system triggered by GitLab Merge Requests

---

### CONTEXT

The team uses LangFuse for tracing, observability, and prompt management.
Developers work on personal/feature-branch LangFuse prompts (named by convention, 
e.g., `feat/my-feature--prompt-name`). When a GitLab MR is merged, the corresponding 
LangFuse prompts must be automatically promoted/merged into the production prompt 
(e.g., `prompt-name` in the `production` label).

